[CITE@@en[XHTML&#8482; Modularization 1.1]] ([CODE[2008-08-14 01:44:58 +09:00]] 版) <http://www.w3.org/MarkUp/2008/ED-xhtml-modularization-20080813/>
([[名無しさん]])

